drop table tx1	0	Execute: java.sql.SQLSyntaxErrorException: (conn=28) Unknown table 'connect.tx1'
Warnings:
Warning	1105	Execute: java.sql.SQLSyntaxErrorException: (conn=28) Unknown table 'connect.tx1'
